node.text:
Let’s kick off the ‘5 THINGS I LOVE’ series with one of the most iconic cars in the fleet, the SLS AMG Black Series! 
Let me know in the comments what you love the most about the car!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on September 02, 2021 tagging @shmee150wastaken, @theshmeemobiles, and @theshmuseum. May be an image of car.

node.text: How about this for @theshmeemobiles group test! 1) My 'first car' 2) The first car to be called Shmeemobile 3) The ultimate member of my garage. Three very different eras of my car ownership, three very memorable periods, and three cars that are fantastic to now keep together under one roof at @theshmuseum #Renault #Clio #AstonMartin #Vantage #McLaren #Senna #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 31, 2021 tagging @ebay_uk, @shmee150wastaken, @theshmeemobiles, and @theshmuseum. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: There's a surprise addition to @theshmeemobiles! Via @ebay_uk Motors, I've bought an identical 2005 Renault Clio 1.2 Dynamique to the first car I ever owned over 15 years ago. Since acquiring the scrap metal wreck of my actual first car, I've been looking for a matching twin to add to the collection and now that I've picked this up, it's time to do something big! Working with small businesses on eBay, we're going to turn this into a sleeper track tool; I'm thinking engine swap, interior strip out, and much more. There are lots of small businesses out there selling many parts that are going to make this really something cool. The spec of this car is the same as my original one down to the wheels, interior trim, and even the sunroof and auto lights, let's do this! #Renault #Clio #eBay #Shmeemobile #newcar #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 30, 2021 tagging @shmee150wastaken, and @automobilipininfarinaofficial. May be an image of 1 person, car and road.

node.text: I'm discovering the new @automobilipininfarinaofficial Battista in full visual carbon! The team have engineered a 'Pure sound' that introduces audible characteristics in the car's different driving modes to bring character to the otherwise silent EV hypercar. I'm hopping on board for a ride to learn all about it with the first production ready car, with deliveries of the first customer cars coming not too long from now, and 150 in total to be made. #Pininfarina #Battista #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 28, 2021 tagging @chartwell_derby, @shmee150wastaken, and @theshmeemobiles. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: This is @theshmeemobiles AMG GT Black Series! The car has been nearly fully stripped down at @chartwell_derby ready for the complete colour change to AMG Solarbeam, and that means some serious work. It's quite shocking to see the car mid way through the process but with the majority already removed, the surfaces can be prepped and very soon the change to yellow will commence, and I cannot wait! #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.text: Lucky to visit @garage26, an extraordinary private collection of Ferrari and Porsche supercars. From the striking LaFerrari Aperta, through the Ferrari hypercar timeline, and many more stand out models like the SA Aperta and a full trio of Ruf CTRs. The collection is born out of a family passion and carries beyond just the cars, presented in immaculate settings. Thank you for the visit and thank you to @jgpv.speed for making arrangements #Ferrari #LaFerrari #LaFerrariAperta #Garage26 #Miamicars #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 25, 2021 tagging @dragtimescom, @racepbir, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of one or more people, car and road.

node.text: Went to the drag strip with @dragtimescom and the new Model S Plaid... was not disappointed! This thing is a rocketship, low 9s with ease, it's just mind blowing to be honest. After a drive up, a Supercharger stop to get it to 100% for the drags, and then some flat out launches at @racepbir there's certainly a stage of trying to evaluate and make sense of the acceleration! #Tesla #ModelS #Plaid #DragTimes #PBIR #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 23, 2021 tagging @dan_am_i, @koenigsegg, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: Checking out @dan_am_i's Koenigsegg Regera Honey! Not only is this the first hypercar with an NFT attached, but it also has a scannable logo that will play a video by Christian von Koenigsegg and a song by his son, Sebastian, plus it was launched with a live stream I joined on @lemonade.tv too. It's finished in a full exposed carbon body with diamond dust in the lacquer and Monterey Blue accents to finish it off. Safe to say there are plenty of other awesome cars in the mancave with @speedy_jeff @x_marc_the_spot #Koenigsegg #Regera #Honey #LAcars #testdrive #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 22, 2021 tagging @hennesseyperformance, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person, outdoors and text that says 'MAMMOTH S'.

node.text: Checking out the @hennesseyperformance Mammoth 1000 hypertruck! The most powerful truck they've made, based on the RAM TRX, limited to 200 cars, and this features the full Stage II package with new upgraded bumpers and the wheels with 37" off-road tires. Time to go drive in road and get lost off the beaten track #Hennessey #Mammoth #RAM1500 #TRX #testdrive #LAcars #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 20, 2021 tagging @philwilson, @shmee150wastaken, and @bannedauto. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: Back at the wheel of an SF90! With @bannedauto and @philwilson I'm checking out this stunning Assetto Fiorano car and thinking about the final spec I'll opt for mine, which actually needs to be locked next month. I'm also delighted to say that again the car has impressed me, I think it's one of the very best supercars currently on the market, mixing insane performance with new technology in such a seamless way. Needless to say, I'm quite excited about it! #Ferrari #SF90 #futureshmeemobile #AssettoFiorano #BannedAuto #LAcars #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on August 17, 2021 tagging @ct2go, @shmee150wastaken, and @supercarsteven. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: It's a P1 kinda day! Out for a drive in @supercarsteven's newly purchased Ice Silver P1, in a double convoy with @ct2go's full carbon P1 too. Does make me wonder about P1 vs Senna, two very different Ultimate Series cars in their approach, and still remarkable how game changing the P1 was when presented nearly 9 years ago! #McLaren #P1 #McLarenP1 #testdrive #CarWeek #Shmee150
